data.description: This charming 3-bedroom home is ready to welcome you to a serene lifestyle on a generous 1.25-acre lot, free from the constraints of an HOA. Plus, with FHA financing available, your path to homeownership has never been more accessible. Situated on a picturesque hillside lot, this property offers breathtaking mountain views. The interior of the home has been lovingly maintained and recently updated. A brand-new A/C system, just two years old, and fresh interior paint applied just a few days ago, breathes new life into the living spaces. And the kitchen boasts a reverse osmosis system. The property has private well providing a reliable source of water. This offers a rare opportunity to escape the hustle and bustle of city life and embrace the beauty of the natural world!
